name: Pinky Punky #01
description: Pinky Punky #01 is the first member of the monochromes. Crazy girl in magenta tones. 'Monochrome Punks are monochrome graphic style Punks.' Monochrome displays (green and blue graphic ones) were common in cell phones in the late 90s and early 2000s. Are you ready for a journey to 2000s with Monochrome Punky'ies?
